---

# ATLAS AI Intelligence Requirements

The SharePoint repository must provide only raw project delivery data.

ATLAS AI will dynamically calculate:

* Project Health Score
* Project Status
* Release Readiness Score
* Portfolio Health
* Governance Compliance Status
* Risk Severity Analysis
* Resource Risk
* Delivery Risk Forecast
* Leadership Insights
* Executive Recommendations

No calculated intelligence values should be stored in SharePoint.

---

# Security Requirements

All content must remain within Microsoft 365.

No external sources, websites, APIs, or third-party repositories should be used.

The repository should simulate a real enterprise PMO and project governance environment suitable for demonstrating ATLAS AI capabilities.

